description:
Subjects Addressed: (1) Blessed are ye, when men shall revile you, and persecute you…Matthew 5:11,12. Why is this the final beatitude?  
(2) Franklin Graham: We’ve taken God out of government, schools and everything else and we need to use our vote to get God back into it. (14:02)
(3) Pope Francis one by one reclaiming Protestants; he recently joined forces with Methodists to heal wounds. (16:33)
(4) Pope Francis’ “Amoris Laetitia” places culture and tradition above God’s moral law; he states that Sunday Law will solve moral crisis. (21:28)
(5) Bernie Sanders to meet Pope Francis. Both men call for Sunday Law to solve global economic crisis. (38:49)
(6) 16 Democrat Attorney Generals Begin Inquisition Against ‘Climate Change Disbelievers. (47:14)  
(7) Hans von Spakovsky: A new Spanish Inquisition is here for Climate Change Deniers and rejecters of solutions for Climate Change. The Jesuits were behind the Spanish Inquisition and their fingerprints are all over the Climate Change movement. (48:09)
